MOJAC KAT , well placed early, chased the leaders while three wide into the stretch but lacked a solid finish. SPRING THE BEAST was sent up between runners soon after the break, moved to near even terms battling pace the three eighths, drifted out bothering BERNIE'S ON FIRE entering the lane, corrected and gave way. CONFUSION BABY BOY lagged back, was under asking three wide into the stretch but failed to respond.
